# Online Boredom Solution #1: Quick Start Guide for Online Courses

When you find yourself with free time online, online courses offers an
engaging way to transform boredom into valuable skills. This quick start guide
will show you how to get started.

## Getting Started

Begin your online courses journey with these steps:

  * Set clear learning objectives
  * Gather essential tools and resources
  * Create a consistent practice schedule
  * Join relevant online communities

## Continue Your Learning Journey

